    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride that has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved and looked after! It's perfect for anyone looking for a dependable car that still looks and feels great on the road. I've kept up with all the regular maintenance, so it's totally ready for its next adventure with you. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take a look!",
