    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E36 M3 is a mechanically sorted example featuring the S50B30US inline-six, exhibiting strong compression across all cylinders and a recently serviced single-VANOS unit for precise variable valve timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a ZF 5-speed manual gearbox with a refreshed shift linkage and a 3.15:1 limited-slip differential that provides consistent lock-up. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul utilizing an aluminum radiator and a metal-impeller water pump. The chassis has been enhanced with Bilstein B8 dampers and reinforced rear subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. While it shows the honest patina of a driver-focused car, the kinematics and powertrain remain tight and responsive, offering the tactile feedback expected of a true M-division product.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed. Minor cosmetic wear only. Reliable engine. Service records available.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained Graphite Metallic sedan that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, though upon close inspection, you will find a few minor rock chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scuff on the rear passenger door\u2014typical for a well-loved daily driver. The alloy wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring premium black leather upholstery. While there is some light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the seats remain firm and supportive. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and sunroof, functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent synthetic oil change and a multi-point inspection that cleared the brakes and suspension. The transmission shifts seamlessly, and the engine runs quiet and strong. This is a reliable, honest vehicle looking for its next owner who appreciates a car that has been cared for properly.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
