      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. It looks great and drives even better! I've taken good care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love getting behind the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions!",
