    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six engine. This power plant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system to deliver exceptional throttle response across the rev range. Power is managed via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through a limited-slip M-Variable differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a refreshed suspension setup, preserving the precise steering rack feedback and neutral handling balance inherent to the E46 platform. A technically sound specimen for the discerning purist.",
